                                <title type="desc">Stella clericorum</title>
                                <rubric>Quasi stella matutina in medio</rubric>
                                <incipit>Quasi stella matutina in medio nebule</incipit>
                                <explicit>et de salutari medicina sibi miserabiliter acquirunt eternam dampnacionem et sic est finis et cetera</explicit>
                                <finalRubric>Explicit stella clericorum</finalRubric>
                                <note> The colophon is written in smaller script and in a different ink, and possibly by a different hand from the main text. Notable is also that a different decade (<quote>59</quote>) has been written first and then deleted. <!--Hedlund säger samma hand. Jag tycker m och h skiljer sig markant--></note>
                                <colophon>
                                    <locus from="91r" to="91r" scheme="folios"/>Anno domini millesimo cccc<hi rend="super">o</hi>
                                    <del>lviiii</del> xxxviiii<hi rend="super">o</hi> in vigilia beati bartholomei</colophon>
                                <bibl>
                                    <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107427">Reiter (1997)</title>
